00:26.192 --> 00:28.611
-Can I help you?
-Diane Russell, I need
to speak to you.

00:28.611 --> 00:33.074
Angela, this is not Diane's
cup of tea. We want these
male cops involved.

00:33.074 --> 00:35.994
I'm gonna try
not to take that
too personally, Peaches.

00:35.994 --> 00:39.289
Diane, you know
our feelings towards you.
But look at that face.

00:39.289 --> 00:43.418
Angela's gonna be a dead ho
unless we get a strong
male presence involved.

00:43.418 --> 00:45.754
I guess strong
would leave you out?

00:45.754 --> 00:49.382
-So, who hit you, Angela?
-God, you are such a doll.

00:49.382 --> 00:52.802
-Who hit you?
-PEACHES: Could we do
this over doughnuts?

00:52.802 --> 00:54.220
Come on.

00:57.223 --> 01:00.101
-Morning, boss.
-Diane.

01:00.101 --> 01:02.437
-I hope you got those
lemon-filled.
-Don't touch me.

01:06.983 --> 01:10.653
I'll serve, you explain, and
do not go easy on that person.

01:10.653 --> 01:15.700
All right. I've been thinking
about having the operation,
and I decided that I would.

01:15.700 --> 01:19.037
And then I decided that I didn't
want to 'cause I knew this girl.

01:19.037 --> 01:22.290
Last year she went and had it,
but they didn't properly
complete the steps.

01:22.290 --> 01:25.668
She got infected
and complicated,
and she almost died.

01:25.668 --> 01:29.714
Back and forth to the hospital,
still a year later,
nothing works right on her.

01:29.714 --> 01:32.175
So, Angela, this guy
who hit you, or maybe
is looking to do worse,

01:32.175 --> 01:34.344
he wants you
to have this operation?

01:34.344 --> 01:36.638
That is a detective.

01:36.638 --> 01:38.473
(clears throat) Broke bad
when you changed your mind?

01:38.473 --> 01:41.267
To do it right,
you gotta go to Europe,
but he don't want to know.

01:41.267 --> 01:42.102
PEACHES:
Now he's saying
he's gonna cut her throat.

01:42.102 --> 01:43.937
ANGELA:
I don't think he means it.

01:43.937 --> 01:46.689
I saw that man look at you
with murder in his eyes.

01:46.689 --> 01:49.651
I got an idea.
How 'bout you put
a name to this guy,

01:49.651 --> 01:51.736
you sign a complaint,
and we'll go out
and we'll arrest him?

01:51.736 --> 01:53.488
-Complaint?
-Yes, a complaint, Angela.

01:53.488 --> 01:56.658
What do you think this is,
a counseling service? File
a complaint, we arrest him.

01:56.658 --> 01:59.577
-I never said arrest.
-PEACHES:
Arrest is too strong.

01:59.577 --> 02:02.497
You guys gotta go out
there and shake him up.
Can you smack him?

02:02.497 --> 02:05.125
-I don't want him smacked.
-Girl, look what he did to you!

02:05.125 --> 02:07.710
Give up the name or
take a walk, Angela.

02:07.710 --> 02:12.257
-You gotta put him in jail?
-You give up a name
and his usual places,

02:12.257 --> 02:13.341
and then we decide what we do.

02:13.341 --> 02:15.802
Do you realize what this
morning is gonna be like?

02:15.802 --> 02:17.554
You can come
with us on this.

02:17.554 --> 02:19.889
I think it needs
a strong male presence.

02:19.889 --> 02:21.891
(sighs, coughs)

02:21.891 --> 02:25.603
-(sobs)
-Got her head on the notebook.

02:26.604 --> 02:30.859
Here, lift your
head there, Angela.

02:30.859 --> 02:33.945
-Jimmy Cortez.
-Puerto Rican muscleman.

02:33.945 --> 02:37.532
Won't accept
a person for herself or
his own nature neither.

02:37.532 --> 02:39.742
You should have your
own talk show, Peaches.

02:39.742 --> 02:42.537
