(paper bag rustling)

06:02.945 --> 06:04.614
Come on in, folks.

06:09.160 --> 06:11.496
-Lucy always liked Jill.
-Fine.

06:13.664 --> 06:15.208
Please.

06:21.255 --> 06:24.217
