Wrong apartment.
-(door buzzing)

08:02.273 --> 08:04.942
Jimmy Cortez?
Jimmy?

08:04.942 --> 08:10.072
(sighs)
Ah--

08:10.072 --> 08:13.659
Moron broad don't
write the apartment down?

08:13.659 --> 08:15.453
I like that
you call her a woman.

08:15.453 --> 08:18.873
I take 'em as I find 'em.
Try not to look
between their legs.

08:18.873 --> 08:22.335
We got to check out 1A and
1B when we come back--Andy.

08:27.089 --> 08:30.510
-Hey. What's your name?
-What's that to you?

08:30.510 --> 08:33.554
-See that right there?
Tell me your name.
-Jimmy Cortez.

08:33.554 --> 08:37.350
Jimmy Cortez. All right,
Jimmy, let's go talk
in the hallway, here, huh?

08:37.350 --> 08:41.604
What, so you can kick my ass,
no witnesses? You want to talk
to me, let's talk right here.

08:41.604 --> 08:47.693
-All right, your call.
-You datin' a person
named Angela?

08:47.693 --> 08:50.488
What, that bitch made
a complaint on me? Huh?

08:50.488 --> 08:54.492
-She came complaining on me?
-Tends to happen when
you smack 'em in the face.

08:54.492 --> 08:58.538
Look, I didn't know that was
a man. Okay, you see her? Tits
out to here, cute little ass.

08:58.538 --> 09:01.082
-How you supposed to know?
-Hey, Jimmy. No one
is jammin' you up...

09:01.082 --> 09:05.086
-for confusing her sex, okay?
-Smacking her in the head's
what aroused the concern.

09:05.086 --> 09:07.922
-What's going on?
-Now everybody's
got to know about this.

09:07.922 --> 09:10.758
You're worried about
the wrong thing here, Jimmy.

09:10.758 --> 09:13.553
Nobody wants to do a lot
of paperwork on you,

09:13.553 --> 09:18.391
but you lay hands on this
Angela again, and you're gonna
get collared and brought in.

09:18.391 --> 09:21.769
-What'd she do for you?
-Oh, yeah, yeah. Yeah,
that's right, Jimmy. Yeah.

09:21.769 --> 09:24.855
-Her and us, we've been
having, like, secret trysts.
-Jimmy, yes or no.

09:24.855 --> 09:26.607
-Are you gonna stay away
from this Angela?
-(scoffs)

09:26.607 --> 09:28.901
-I'm not a fag.
You got that?
-All right.

09:28.901 --> 09:32.363
If we agree you're
not a fag, are you gonna
stay away from Angela?

09:32.363 --> 09:36.367
-She's deep inside me, man.
-What the hell are we doing?
Come on, you're coming inside.

09:36.367 --> 09:38.995
-Nah, Nah.
I'll stay away, man.
-Square business on this.

09:38.995 --> 09:40.162
You don't want to be hurtin'
her.

09:40.162 --> 09:43.040
Even if somebody else
hurts her, we're coming after
you.

09:43.040 --> 09:45.418
-I got ya. I'll stay away.
-Hmm?

09:53.801 --> 09:56.679
-Deep inside him.
-That guy's trouble.

09:56.679 --> 10:00.474
