jewelry and a Mont Blanc pen
sold by Miss Hastings.

13:52.039 --> 13:53.791
Well, I-I got behind
in my paperwork.

13:53.791 --> 13:56.794
-Have you still got
those things, Mr. Babcock?
-Yeah, I got them.

13:56.794 --> 14:00.256
-And nonspecific urethritis.
-All right, you know what?
I'm gonna wait outside.

14:00.256 --> 14:02.258
-Lucy!
